Introducing our 24x48 Gemma Mattia Marble Look Glossy Porcelain Tile, a blend of elegance and durability for your home. Featuring the timeless grace of marble and the resilience of porcelain, this large format tile offers the perfect balance of luxury and practicality.

  • With its glossy finish and multi-faceted design, this tile effortlessly elevates any space, from bathrooms to kitchens, living rooms to bedrooms.
  • Designed for those who appreciate the beauty of marble but seek a low maintenance, cost-effective alternative, our Gemma Mattia tile is the ideal choice.
  • Experience the long-lasting quality of porcelain, combined with the versatility and functionality of marble, creating a reliable solution for your home.

Transform your space with the sophistication of marble and the reliability of porcelain, all in one exquisite tile. Easy to maintain and stunning to behold, our Gemma Mattia tile is a statement of style and substance.

Upgrade your home with the premium quality and enduring allure of our Gemma Mattia Marble Look Glossy Porcelain Tile. Make a lasting impression with every step. Order now and elevate your space with opulence and longevity.

SPECIFICATIONS
ADDITIONAL DETAILS

Recommended Overage

  • Don’t forget to add the overage you will need for cuts, waste, breaks, and future repairs. The standard overage we recommend is 10%.

Sample Information

  • We strongly recommend ordering a sample before placing a large order. Tile is subject to standard variances resulting from the manufacturing process. All products are within the industry standard variance levels. Additionally, while we strive to provide accurate professional photography, colors may appear different due to variations in cameras, lighting, and screen displays.
  • Sample sizes vary depending on the product, and typically come as a small section of the product.
  • When ordering a sample of this product a swatch sample will be sent as a sample. Swatch sizes are usually 3"x6", 4"x4", 6"x6" or 8"x8".
  • 2 sample of the same item is allowed per household/address.
  • Samples are not returnable.

Shipping Information

  • Shipping is available within contiguous United States, with limited item availability for shipments to Alaska and Hawaii.
  • Special arrangements can be made for customers from Canada, please contact us to get a quote.
  • For large orders and all other shipping-related inquiries, please contact our shipping department.

Ship / Lead Time

  • Normally ships within 1-2 Business days.

Item Location / Local Pickup

  • Items are located in Southern California (Anaheim, CA).
  • You can choose the "Pickup in store" option during checkout.
  • Local pickup is available by appointment only, and same-day pickups are not offered.

Disclaimer

  • Please keep in mind that items under Tile (whether porcelain, ceramic, glass, or terrazzo) or Performance Flooring (vinyl, laminate, or hardwood) may exhibit slight variations in color, texture, and finish due to manufacturing processes. Expect to have some variation between individual pieces when ordering in large quantities.
